#new:Function $Function_GetTattle
{
LIO       V0, $Tattle
JR        RA
RESERVED
}


#new:String $Tattle
{
[Style Tattle]
Seems like a side room.[BR]
[Pause 5]This is definitely no time to get[BR]
side-tracked, Mario.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I'm still dying to know where the[BR]
hotties are at in this dungeon.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Speaking of hot, this place is a[BR]
heck of a lot cooler than it is[BR]
outside. [Pause 15]Thank God.[Wait][End]
}